      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      120                  to   w-all-str-lun          .
           move      04                   to   w-all-str-num          .
           move      w-acc-ser-edd-rtr (1)
                                          to   w-all-str-cat (1)      .
           move      w-acc-ser-edd-rtr (2)
                                          to   w-all-str-cat (2)      .
