      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      v-dat                to   w-tes-dat-vld          .
       acc-dat-vld-400.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Controllo valore impostato                      *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
       acc-dat-vld-600.
